OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1773076276
OL,3,C7-year-old boy dies after being hit by
OL,4,Ccar on A38 near Lichfield
OL,6,FA 7-year-old boy has died after being
OL,7,Fhit by a car on the A38 near Lichfield.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,10,Freport of a collision between a car
OL,11,Fand a child on the A38 at the junction
OL,12,Fwith the A5206 at around 5am this
OL,13,Fmorning (Saturday).
OL,15,FThe child, a boy aged 7, died at the
OL,16,Fscene. His family has been informed
OL,17,Fand are being supported by specially-
OL,18,Ftrained officers.
