OL,3,C7-year-old boy dies after being hit by
OL,4,Ccar on A38 near Lichfield
OL,6,FStaffordshire Police say to help with
OL,7,Ftheir investigation, the A38 remains
OL,8,Fclosed in both directions between the
OL,9,FA5148 and A5 junctions, although this
OL,10,Fis expected to be reopened shortly.
OL,12,FThey are keen to speak to anyone who
OL,13,Fwas travelling in the area with any
OL,14,Finformation or dashcam footage which
OL,15,Fcould help collision investigators.
